snippet.title: OstrichIsland XboxOne version
snippet.description:
http://medungeon.com

Volcano erupts! All archipelago residents have been evacuated, but one ostrich had his head in the sand. Can you help him escape and rejoin his family?

The game is the unique adventure/exploration/RPG mix where you play as an Ostrich! Walk into tropical paradise, rush through storm madness, explore the deepness of the ocean and behold the darkness of underground. Each island contains many secret achievements, collectibles and bonuses wanted to be discovered!
